- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms): The paper develops a new algorithmic property called one-step differential stability, which is related to data structures and algorithms. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper discusses online learning methods, which are a subset of artificial intelligence.
